RAEEN-LINUXKPI-FIRMWARE-SELFTEST-BLOB-v1
This blob exists only to exercise request_firmware (syscall 142) end-to-end in
QEMU: the kernel loads firmware/<name> from the initramfs and maps it into the
calling driver daemon. Real driver microcode (amdgpu gc_*.bin, iwlwifi *.ucode)
is dropped into this firmware/ directory the same way.
